  "title": "Banking Admin & Fee Waiver [Contact Centre - Customer Service Fulfilment Operations]",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manages and handle incoming &amp; outgoing emails</li>\n  <li>Ensures cases are sent or attended within the standard turnaround or within the agreed turnaround time to customers.</li>\n  <li>Working with team members to ensure the Service Level for Emails, Letters, Faxes Payment Advice and Social Media management are met daily.</li>\n  <li>Render support to submit waiver requests for those waiver cases submitted via IVR</li>\n  <li>Adherence to the rules and guidelines as per the Bank's Code of Conduct and Group Banking Operations Policy when handling emails, faxes, letters, processing requests and Social media management.</li>\n</ul>",
